{"id":20,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22623,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":20,"title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","subtitle":"","short_title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.head1"},[".title","The New Adventures of Matt & Mandy"]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f1"},[".credit",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p2"},"Illustrations by Maryn Roos"]],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p3"},"What’s going on?"]],["div",{"id":"f2","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f2"},["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p4"},"Shhh! Let’s go talk in my room."]],["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f3"},["div",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p5"},"Don’t you think Mom and Dad have been acting weird lately?"],["div",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p6"},"Yeah. Sometimes when I come into the room they stop talking."]],["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f4"},["div",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p7"},"Last night when I got up for a drink of water—I mean, it was really late— they were in the kitchen whispering and looking at some papers."]],["div",{"id":"f5","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f5"},["div",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p8"},"I tried to find out what’s going on. The other day I asked Mom if she’s mad at me. Or if somebody’s sick or something."]],["div",{"id":"f6","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f6"},["div",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p9"},"What did she say?"],["div",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p10"},"She said nobody’s sick, I’m not in trouble, and nothing’s wrong. Of course I didn’t ask if",["span.emphasis","you"],"are in trouble …"]],["div",{"id":"f7","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f7"},["div",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p11"},"You’re",["span.emphasis","so"],"funny."]],["div",{"id":"f8","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f8"},["div",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p12"},"C’mon, didn’t she tell you anything?"],["div",{"id":"p13","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p13"},"She said there’s nothing to worry about. They just aren’t ready to talk about it yet. I still don’t know what’s going on, but I kinda feel like everything’s OK."],["div",{"id":"p14","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p14"},"Why?"]],["div",{"id":"f9","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f9"},["div",{"id":"p15","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p15"},"Well, for one thing, I believe Mom. Plus, I’ve been praying about it, and … I dunno … I just feel more peaceful."]],["div",{"id":"f10","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f10"},["div",{"id":"p16","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p16"},"Kids, could you two come in the kitchen for a minute?"]],["div",{"id":"f11","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f11"},["div",{"id":"p17","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p17"},"We know you’ve been wondering what’s going on. Well, now we can finally tell you the exciting news."]],["div",{"id":"p18","uri":"/friend/2013/01/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p18"},"(To be continued next month.)"]]],"refs":null}
